section.para:
In the basic setting, the export is performed every 15 minutes by a cron job and is
additionally started if the &ucsUDL; has been inactive for 15
seconds. The interval for the cron update is configured in Cron syntax (see ) by the &ucsUCRV;
nss/group/cachefile/invalidate_interval. This listener module can be
activated/deactivated via the &ucsUCRV;
nss/group/invalidate_cache_on_changes (true/false).
